overview: The user wanted to significantly improve the aesthetics of their sleep
  questionnaire app, moving it from a generic look to a more beautiful and
  professional design. The assistant undertook a comprehensive review,
  identifying areas like the color palette, layout, and individual component
  styling as needing improvement. The approach involved defining a new calming,
  sleep-themed color palette, applying subtle background elements, and
  redesigning the main form, progress indicator, and welcome section. All 14
  form sections were updated to use consistent, refined card-style groupings and
  theme colors for form fields like checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders. The
  outcome is an app with a cohesive, calming, and professional visual language,
  enhancing the user experience for a sleep health assessment.
